        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Da Jung, the youngest team supervisor at her company, is known for her fiery temper and three divorces, making her a subject of suspicion and disdain. She is tough and indifferent to others' opinions. In contrast, Jung Gi is a gentle, passive man, often seen as a pushover. After a series of events, Da Jung becomes Jung Gi's boss, and her tyrannical leadership turns his life upside down. However, as Jung Gi\n\nnavigates the challenges, his quiet resilience starts to shake things up in the office.",
